   Phase 8 Neural-Kernel Integration Tests: Unforgiving Validation

   40개 무관용 테스트 (4개 모듈 × 10개):
   Group A (A1-A10): L0 Engine - SIMD + Neural Network
   Group B (B1-B10): Hardware Optimizer - DVFS + Thermal
   Group C (C1-C10): Threat Engine - Real-time Prediction
   Group D (D1-D10): Distributed Optimizer - Consensus + Self-Optimization

   목표: 40/40 테스트 통과 (100%)
   8개 무관용 규칙 달성 (100%)
============================================================================ */

